# ============================================================================
# VoiceSnip Configuration
# ============================================================================
#
# VoiceSnip uses local-only STT with GPU acceleration.
# No cloud providers, no API keys required.
#
# ============================================================================
# Settings Persistence
# ============================================================================
# All settings are automatically saved in config.json when you click "Start"
# in the GUI. The last used settings will be restored when you restart the
# application.
#
# Available Providers:
# - whisper-local-gpu: Local Whisper on GPU (Free, requires NVIDIA CUDA)
# - whisper-local-rocm: Local Whisper on GPU (Free, requires AMD ROCm)
#
# Everything (Provider, Model, Language, Microphone, Hotkey) can be
# configured in the GUI!
